<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover, user-scalable=yes, maximum-scale=5">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f766e">
  <meta name="description" content="Zarządzaj ogłoszeniem w TwojBazar.">
  <title>Zarządzaj ogłoszeniem | TwojBazar</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <header class="navbar" id="siteHeader">
      <a href="index.html#start" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-mark">TB</span>
        <span class="logo-text">TwojBazar</span>
      </a>

      <button class="menu-toggle" type="button" aria-label="Otwórz menu" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="site-navigation">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
      <div class="nav-center">
        <nav class="nav-links" id="site-navigation">
          <a href="index.html#start">Start</a>
          <a href="index.html#kategorie">Kategorie</a>
          <a href="pomoc.html">Pomoc</a>
          <a href="index.html#kontakt">Kontakt</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="navbar-cta">
        <a href="add-listing.html" class="nav-cta">Dodaj ogłoszenie</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="subpage-main">
      <section class="add-listing-layout">
        <div class="form-panel">
          <span class="page-kicker">Prywatny link</span>
          <h1 class="page-title">Zarządzaj ogłoszeniem</h1>
          <p class="page-intro" id="manageIntro">Ładowanie danych ogłoszenia...</p>

          <form class="listing-form" id="manageListingForm" novalidate>
            <div class="form-field" data-field="title">
              <label for="manageTitle">Tytuł</label>
              <input id="manageTitle" name="title" type="text">
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-field" data-field="category">
                <label for="manageCategory">Kategoria</label>
                <select id="manageCategory" name="category"></select>
              </div>

              <div class="form-field" data-field="price">
                <label for="managePrice">Cena</label>
                <input id="managePrice" name="price" type="text">
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-field" data-field="country">
                <label for="manageCountry">Kraj</label>
                <select id="manageCountry" name="country">
                  <option value="">Wybierz kraj</option>
                  <option value="Szwecja">Szwecja</option>
                  <option value="Norwegia">Norwegia</option>
                  <option value="Dania">Dania</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div class="form-field" data-field="city">
                <label for="manageCity">Miasto</label>
                <input id="manageCity" name="city" type="text">
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field" data-field="description">
              <label for="manageDescription">Opis</label>
              <textarea id="manageDescription" name="description"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="manageImage">Zdjęcie</label>
              <input id="manageImage" type="file" accept="image/*" class="file-input-native">
              <label for="manageImage" class="file-upload-ui">
                <span class="file-upload-trigger">Wybierz nowe zdjęcie</span>
                <span class="file-upload-status" id="manageImageStatus">Bez zmian</span>
              </label>
              <div class="image-preview hidden" id="manageImagePreview">
                <img id="manageImagePreviewThumb" alt="Podgląd zdjęcia">
                <button type="button" class="image-preview-remove" id="manageRemoveImageButton">Usuń wybrane zdjęcie</button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <section class="form-section" aria-labelledby="manageContactTitle">
              <div class="form-section-header">
                <p class="form-section-kicker">Kontakt</p>
                <h2 id="manageContactTitle">Dane kontaktowe</h2>
              </div>

              <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-field">
                  <label for="manageContactName">Imię kontaktowe</label>
                  <input id="manageContactName" type="text">
                </div>

                <div class="form-field">
                  <label for="managePhone">Telefon</label>
                  <input id="managePhone" type="tel">
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-field">
                <label for="manageEmail">E-mail</label>
                <input id="manageEmail" type="email">
              </div>

              <div class="form-row form-row-compact">
                <label class="checkbox-field" for="manageShowPhone">
                  <input id="manageShowPhone" type="checkbox">
                  <span>Pokaż telefon w ogłoszeniu</span>
                </label>

                <label class="checkbox-field" for="manageShowEmail">
                  <input id="manageShowEmail" type="checkbox">
                  <span>Pokaż e-mail w ogłoszeniu</span>
                </label>
              </div>
            </section>

            <div class="form-actions">
              <button type="submit" class="button button-primary">Zapisz zmiany</button>
              <button type="button" class="button button-secondary" id="toggleStatusButton">Oznacz jako nieaktualne</button>
              <button type="button" class="button button-secondary" id="deleteListingButton">Usuń ogłoszenie</button>
            </div>

            <p class="form-status" id="manageStatus" aria-live="polite"></p>
          </form>
        </div>

        <aside class="info-panel">
          <h2>Twój link do zarządzania</h2>
          <p>Zachowaj ten link. Tylko przez niego można edytować, usunąć lub oznaczyć ogłoszenie jako nieaktualne.</p>
          <div class="listing-details-contact">
            <p id="publicLinkText"></p>
            <p id="manageLinkText"></p>
            <button type="button" class="button button-secondary" id="copyManageLinkButton">Kopiuj link</button>
            <a class="button button-secondary" id="viewListingButton" href="index.html">Zobacz ogłoszenie</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2026 TwojBazar. Wszelkie prawa zastrzeżone.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script src="manage-listing.js"></script>
</body>
</html>



